Developer Terms of Use
des:
This OVBE Biznotes skill, highlights important facts about entrepreneurship, business, and the online community OVBE. It is pronounced (O-V-BE) and is an acronym for opportunity, venture, business, entrepreneur. The focus of OVBE is to promote financial literacy, business, and entrepreneurship. The biznotes include information about, options to start a business, definitions of some business terms, and how joining OVBE can be used as a resource to create your own opportunities.

This OVBE Biznotes skill provides actionable information, motivation, and ideas that can be used to form a business. Once the skill is open, just ask for a "daily biznote", "biznote update", or say, "tell me a biznote" to hear facts about starting a business, entrepreneurship, and what you can do on OVBE.
